adding the user to group in order to access docker from standard user

    sudo usermod -aG docker username

check where the docker installation is placed

    docker infor | grep -i root

check how much space docker is taking

    sudo du -sh /var/lib/docker

adding a permission for jenkins user to write data into the jenkins_home

    chown 1000:1000 jenkins_home -R


starting the docker-compose app (navigate to the folder first)

    docker-compose up -d

to stop

    docker-compose stop

to start again

    docker-compose start


to restart 

    docker-compose restart jenkins